name: Murttoc Yine
Lore: 'Information broker. Spy. Has many nefarious contacts in the underworld. Contact point for many seeking employment with Jabba.',
Text: 'During your control phase, if at a Jabba''s Palace site you control, may use 3 Force to search your Reserve Deck, take one other alien that is a smuggler, information broker, thief or spy into hand and reshuffle.',
